title: Volume of US YouTube shows ‘weakens UK children’s ties to their own culture’
summary: The head of children's TV at BBC has criticized YouTube's algorithm for directing children primarily towards US-based content instead of UK programming. title: Weatherwatch: EU survey gives a few hints on voter-friendly climate policies
